The blog post explains that the request is reaching the server IP on port HTTPS 443
The blog post explains that the traffic is encrypted using HTTPS/SSL certificate
The blog post mentions that the request is answered by a web server serving the page
The blog post explains that the request is distributed by the load-balancer to a web server
The blog post explains that the request is passing through the firewall that accepts traffic on port TCP/443
The blog post explains that the application server will generate the page
The blog post explains that the application server queries the database to gather necessary data

